metadata.bio: Singer, songwriter, producer, and multi-instrumentalist Devin Kennedy invites intimacy through his handcrafted hybrid of alternative and R&B. A Los Angeles native and graduate of Berklee College of Music, Devin weaves his life into the core of his music, opening up so much that youâ€™ll feel like you know him as well as one of your closest friends. Such sonic and lyrical candor has endeared him to a growing fan base, with hundreds of millions of streams independently.
